            That case at least serves as evidence that such things do happen. They happen in all parties&#x2014;this is not a party political point. There have been instances of electoral fraud in all the major parties.</p><p>
            
            <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_455wh' title='Col. 455WH &mdash; HC Deb 05 May 2004 vol 420 c455WH' name='column_455wh' href='#column_455wh' rel='bookmark'>455WH</a>
